# Sonic 1 smoke: boot through Sega + title screen, enter GHZ Act 1,
# run right for ~2800 frames. Mirrors Sonic 2's smoke_enter_level_run_right
# scenario for parallel visual regression coverage.
#
# Game_Mode ($FFF600) transitions:
#   0x00 -> Sega screen
#   0x04 -> title
#   0x0C -> level play (top bit 0x80 is set briefly during the transition)
#
# Single START press at title is enough — Sonic 1 doesn't have Sonic 2's
# intro-animation skip step.

WAIT 480
PRESS START 2
WAIT_RAM8 FFF600 8C
WAIT_RAM8 FFF600 0C
WAIT 30
HOLD RIGHT
WAIT 2800
EXIT 0
